query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND (chn.name like '%Beatrix Kiddo%' OR chn.name like '%Hermione Granger%') AND it.info in ('votes distribution','LD audio quality','LD pressing plant','where now','top 250 rank','keywords','LD video quality') AND (rt.role like '%BEF%' OR rt.role like '%Samantha Mashaw%' OR rt.role like '%Mike Sutton%') AND (pi.note like '%Kara Stevenson, Journalist%' OR pi.note like '%Samson Yee%') AND it3.info in ('LD sharpness','death notes','color info','genres','copyright holder') AND (t.title like '%guitar%' OR t.title like '%story%' OR t.title like '%love%' OR t.title like '%star%') AND mi.info not in ('Inuktitut','Latvian','French','Tlingit','Japanese','German','Irish Gaelic','Indonesian','Greek','Estonian','Brazilian Sign Language') AND cn.country_code in ('gp','ro','za','ma','ke','suhh','au','sz','bi','as','gn') AND (cn.name like '%Sony Pictures Entertainment%' OR cn.name like '%Lionsgate%' OR cn.name like '%STX%' OR cn.name like '%Working Title Films%') AND cct1.kind not in ('complete+verified','complete') AND cct2.kind in ('complete','crew','cast') AND (mc.note like '%International%' OR mc.note like '%Brazil%' OR mc.note like '%China%' OR mc.note like '%Russia%' OR mc.note like '%Denmark%' OR mc.note like '%UK%') AND k.keyword not like '%justice%' AND k.keyword not like '%evil%' AND k.keyword not like '%paranormal%' AND k.keyword not like '%futuristic%' AND (n.name like '%B%' OR n.name like '%m%') AND n.gender not in ('m')
